ogia) + Pilar 4 (Ritual) — Whole Sign + Rising>Sol>Lua + bundle semanal lunar |\n| 2026-06-10 | cot-20260610-tzolkin-position | Tzolkin = inspiração estrutural Pilar 4 + MAIOR aviso ético (Dreamspell = apropriação; 5 compromissos éticos) |\n\n---\n\n## Arquivos Gerados até Agora\n\n```\n.autonomous/research/\n├── INDEX.md                        ← este arquivo\n├── systems/\n│   ├── gene-keys.md                ✅ (R-001)\n│   ├── human-design.md             ✅ (R-002)\n│   ├── mbti-jung.md                ✅ (R-003)\n│   ├── enneagram.md                ✅ (R-004)\n│   ├── costar.md                   ✅ (R-005)\n│   ├── kabbalah.md                 ✅ (R-008)\n│   ├── cabalistic-numerology.md    ✅ (R-009)\n│   ├── the-pattern.md              ✅ (R-006)\n│   └── chani-app.md                 ✅ (R-007)\n│   └── tzolkin.md                   ✅ (R-010)\n└── chain-of-thought/\n    ├── cot-20260610-gene-keys-synthesis.md\n    ├── cot-20260610-human-design-synthesis.md\n    ├── cot-20260610-mbti-jung-position.md\n    ├── cot-20260610-enneagram-position.md\n    ├── cot-20260610-costar-position.md\n    ├── cot-20260610-kabbalah-position.md\n    ├── cot-20260610-cabalistic-numerology-position.md\n    └── cot-20260610-the-pattern-position.md\n    └── cot-20260610-chani-app-position.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## Próximo Passo\n\n**RQ-010 — Tzolkin / Mayan Calendar** (P2) — sistema de ciclos alternativo ao lunar. Inspiração para Mural temporal (Pilar 4). 30 min.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":82,"oldLines":6,"newStart":82,"newLines":7,"lines":["     ├── cot-20260610-cabalistic-numerology-position.md","     └── cot-20260610-the-pattern-position.md","     └── cot-20260610-chani-app-position.md","+    └── cot-20260610-tzolkin-position.md"," ```"," "," ---"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
